### Variables (optional)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5064
@contentType = application/json

### Get all products
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Product

### Get specific product
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Product/1

### Create new product
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Product
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

